<i>adverb</i>: 풍족히 [풍조키], 풍성히 [풍성히], 풍부히 [풍부히], 푸짐히 [푸짐히] <br>
<ul><li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>풍족히 [풍조키]</dt><br>
<dd>abundantly; plentifully; richly</dd><br>
<dd>매우 넉넉해서 부족함이 없이.</dd><br>
<dd>In enough and ample quantity, without a shortage.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>풍성히 [풍성히]</dt><br>
<dd>abundantly; plentifully; amply</dd><br>
<dd>넉넉하고 많이.</dd><br>
<dd>In plenty, in an abundant quantity.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>풍부히 [풍부히]</dt><br>
<dd>richly; abundantly</dd><br>
<dd>넉넉하고 많게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a sufficient quantity, plenty.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>푸짐히 [푸짐히]</dt><br>
<dd>plentifully; abundantly; generously</dd><br>
<dd>마음이 흐뭇하도록 넉넉하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In an ample quantity, to one's satisfaction.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>